Package: sardine
Type: Package
Title: Structured Architecture for Research Data Integration and Evaluation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jack", "Manners", email = "jack.manners@flinders.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a structured, object-oriented interface for research data integration
    and evaluation, with initial focus on 'REDCap' (Research Electronic Data Capture) API 
    integration. The package facilitates secure and efficient data exchange between R and 
    various research data platforms through modern, cached project objects and comprehensive 
    reporting capabilities.
